 "remarks": "Welcome to 50 Aiken Street #433, a beautifully renovated 1-bedroom, 1.5-bath condo in Rolling Ridge, one of Norwalk&apos;s most well-maintained communities. Step inside to a bright, open-concept living and dining area with a dedicated study space -- all flowing seamlessly to a private balcony perfect for morning coffee or evening relaxation. The kitchen has been completely transformed with brand new LG appliances (dishwasher, electric stove/oven, refrigerator), new cabinets, stainless steel faucet, fresh countertop, and vinyl flooring. The primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and shares access to a fully updated bathroom with new toilet, vanity, mirrors, lighting fixtures, and tile flooring. A powder room off the entry provides convenience for guests. Recent upgrades include new carpet, fresh paint throughout, new AC, and updated lighting fixtures -- move-in ready and meticulously cared for. In-unit laundry adds everyday convenience. Rolling Ridge offers resort-style amenities including pool, clubhouse, tennis courts, and dog park, with HOA covering heat, hot water, water, sewer, trash, snow removal, and grounds maintenance. Located just off Main Avenue, you&apos;re minutes from restaurants, grocery stores, and everything Norwalk has to offer. This is a rare opportunity to own a fully renovated home in a community that truly delivers.",
